 Magnus set up the council table. It could fit 10 bots. That should be a 
sufficent number. He thought of how magmatron had arrived. He knew he would 
need his help but all the pain and the friends he had lost to his evil deeds. 
But they faced a bigger threat now.He sent a comm to Kit Kat.."Hurry Kit Kat. 
The time is near get all the pred troops here. I will round up the primals 
and destrons. We will all meet in the council chamber."
